   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Local Cooperation Fund (LCF) in Paraguay</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Project conducts the Center of Civic Education&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s educational program about democracy (&quot;Project citizen&quot;) through distance teaching. The aim is to promote pupils&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99; learning of concepts of democracy and stimulate their interest towards societal questions and civil acting by training teachers about these matters. Through this training teachers&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99; will gain skills and tools to awake interest in pupils towards societal issues. Implementation of the program from distance enables greater number of participants as teachers can participate easily without losing classes. The fundamental aim of the project is to encourage proactive and socially responsible culture of participation within pupils.</narrative>
  </description>
